# Find PolyVox includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  POLYVOX_INCLUDE_DIR
#  POLYVOX_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use PolyVox.
#  POLYVOX_LIB_DIR, the location of the libraries
#  POLYVOX_FOUND, If false, do not try to use PolyVox
